006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.constraint;
007
008import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
009
010/**
011 *
012 * Supports a visitor pattern over constraint instances.
013 *
014 * @param <T>
015 *          the Java type of a state object passed to the visitor
016 * @param <R>
017 *          the Java type of the result returned by the visitor methods
018 */
019public interface IConstraintVisitor<T, R> {
020
021  /**
022   * Implementation of this method support visitation of an
023   * {@link IAllowedValuesConstraint}.
024   *
025   * @param constraint
026   *          the constraint to visit
027   * @param state
028   *          a state object passed to the visitor
029   * @return the visitation result
030   */
031  R visitAllowedValues(@NonNull IAllowedValuesConstraint constraint, T state);
032
033  /**
034   * Implementation of this method support visitation of an
035   * {@link ICardinalityConstraint}.
036   *
037   * @param constraint
038   *          the constraint to visit
039   * @param state
040   *          a state object passed to the visitor
041   * @return the visitation result
042   */
043  R visitCardinalityConstraint(@NonNull ICardinalityConstraint constraint, T state);
044
045  /**
046   * Implementation of this method support visitation of an
047   * {@link IExpectConstraint}.
048   *
049   * @param constraint
050   *          the constraint to visit
051   * @param state
052   *          a state object passed to the visitor
053   * @return the visitation result
054   */
055  R visitExpectConstraint(@NonNull IExpectConstraint constraint, T state);
056
057  /**
058   * Implementation of this method support visitation of an
059   * {@link IMatchesConstraint}.
060   *
061   * @param constraint
062   *          the constraint to visit
063   * @param state
064   *          a state object passed to the visitor
065   * @return the visitation result
066   */
067  R visitMatchesConstraint(@NonNull IMatchesConstraint constraint, T state);
068
069  /**
070   * Implementation of this method support visitation of an
071   * {@link IIndexConstraint}.
072   *
073   * @param constraint
074   *          the constraint to visit
075   * @param state
076   *          a state object passed to the visitor
077   * @return the visitation result
078   */
079  R visitIndexConstraint(@NonNull IIndexConstraint constraint, T state);
080
081  /**
082   * Implementation of this method support visitation of an
083   * {@link IIndexHasKeyConstraint}.
084   *
085   * @param constraint
086   *          the constraint to visit
087   * @param state
088   *          a state object passed to the visitor
089   * @return the visitation result
090   */
091  R visitIndexHasKeyConstraint(@NonNull IIndexHasKeyConstraint constraint, T state);
092
093  /**
094   * Implementation of this method support visitation of an
095   * {@link IUniqueConstraint}.
096   *
097   * @param constraint
098   *          the constraint to visit
099   * @param state
100   *          a state object passed to the visitor
101   * @return the visitation result
102   */
103  R visitUniqueConstraint(@NonNull IUniqueConstraint constraint, T state);
104}
